{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 12601,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　用があるなら貴様が来い」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "If you have business, come yourself."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12602,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はっはっは。そうしたかったが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ha ha ha. I wanted to, but"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12603,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　形式が必要な事もある。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "sometimes formality is necessary."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12604,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　今回は許してくれ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Please forgive me this time.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12605,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「私の友たるランス殿には、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"To Lord Rance, my friend,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12606,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　特に是非来て欲しくてな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I especially wanted you to come.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12607,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ぶっ殺すぞ、気色の悪い。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I'll kill you, you disgusting bastard."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12608,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　さっさと用件を言え」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Get to the point quickly.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12609,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「くっ、あいつ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Kuh, that guy...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12610,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「抑えて。ガンジー様が話されるわ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hold on. Lord Gandhi will speak.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12611,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うむ……では話すこととしよう」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Very well... then I shall speak.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12612,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "やや改まった様子で、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "With a somewhat formal demeanor,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12613,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ガンジーは少し襟元をただした。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Gandhi adjusted his collar slightly."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12614,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「私はゼスの王族として生まれ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I was born as royalty of Zeth..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12615,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　様々に責務があった」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and had various duties.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12616,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「国をより良く変え、悪を誅し……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"To better the country, punish evil..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12617,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なにより、人類を団結させて魔人より守る。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Above all, to unite humanity and protect them from demons."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12618,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そうした大義に、己を捧げてきたつもりだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I have intended to dedicate myself to such a great cause.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12619,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「しかし現在、そうした責務は、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"However, currently, such responsibilities"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12620,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　私が背負う必要は無くなりつつある。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "are gradually no longer mine to bear."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12621,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　非常時ではあるが、それは喜ばしい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Though it is a time of crisis, that is a fortunate thing.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12622,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「父としても、どれほど務めることができたかは",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"As a father, I do not know how well I have served,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12623,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　分からんが、マジックも人の親になった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "but Magic has also become a parent."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12624,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　一段落ではあるだろう」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It should be a settling of matters.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12625,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "（何かしら……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "(Something..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12626,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　とんでもない事を言い出しそうだわ……）",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "He looks about to say something outrageous...)"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12627,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「おいコラ、前置きはいいんだ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hey, enough with the introduction."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12628,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　くだらん話なら帰るぞ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "If it's nonsense, I'm leaving.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12629,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うむ……そうだな。まあ、端的に話す。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm... yes. Well, I'll speak plainly."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12630,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　私も身辺が落ち着いた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "My affairs have settled."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12631,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　一個人として生きてもいいかと思うのだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I think I might live as an individual now.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12632,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「というわけで……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Therefore..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12633,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　このラグナロックアーク・スーパー・ガンジー。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "this Ragnarokk Arc Super Gandhi"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12634,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　明日、再婚しようと思う」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "intends to remarry tomorrow.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12635,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「―――――――は？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"--------- What?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12636,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「………………へ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"......... Huh?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12637,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「………………あぁ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\".......... What?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12638,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "空気が、固まった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The atmosphere stiffened."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12639,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「え……ええ、と。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Uh... well."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12640,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　再婚……………ですか？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Remarriage... is that so?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12641,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うむ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Indeed.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12642,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「は……は、はああああぁぁぁぁぁっ！？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ha... ha, haaahhhh!?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12643,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いきなり何を言い出すんだお前は！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "What are you suddenly talking about!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12644,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「わ…………そうなんですか。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Wha... is that true?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12645,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　王子……いえ、王様が……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The prince... no, the king is...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12646,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それはそれは、おめでとうございますじゃ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well, well, congratulations.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12647,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ガッ、ガンジー様……が、え、ぁ……？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"G-Gandhi-sama... w-what...?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12648,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　カ、カオル……カオルは……？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Ka-Kaoru... what about Kaoru...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12649,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………初耳よ。完全に」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"This is the first time I've heard of it. Completely.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12650,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なっ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Wha-"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12651,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "くっ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Guh,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12652,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "が、ッ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Gah...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12653,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あーーーーーーーーーー！！！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Aaaaaaahhhhhhh!!!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12654,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どこからつっこめばいいのよ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Where do I even start?!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12655,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふぅむ。反対か？　マジック」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmmm. Are you opposed, Magic?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12656,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そういうことじゃなーーーーい！！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That's not what I meanーーー!!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12657,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんでそういう事を勝手に進めんのよ、親父は！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Why do you go ahead and do things like that on your own, old man!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12658,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「もちろん、王位や王家には",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Of course, concerning the throne and the royal family,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12659,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　問題が残らないようにするとも」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I will make sure no problems remain.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12660,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああもう、そうじゃなくて……！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, no, that's not what I mean...!"
    }
  ]
}

